name: Insect invasion
description:
a few days ago my son asked to be taught to make animation in procreate, I only taught the basics because I'm also still learning. 
today I was surprised to see the results of my son's work, a little horrified but I am very proud.
my son zacky is 9 years old.
now he wants a new ipad to draw, so help him achieve that. :)
